## Construction (lines 1297–1384)

### Pool sizing pass (1297–1310)

```1297:1310:D:\Code\swg-client-v2\src\engine\client\library\clientSkeletalAnimation\src\shared\appearance\SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp
	// account for transform weight data
	int vertexIndex;
	int numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs=0;
	for (vertexIndex = 0; vertexIndex < m_vertexCount; ++vertexIndex)
	{
		const MeshConstructionHelper::VertexData &vertexData = mesh.getVertexData(meshPerShaderData, vertexIndex);
		const int localVertexTransformCount = mesh.getVertexTransformCount(vertexData);
		if (localVertexTransformCount>1)
		{
			numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs += localVertexTransformCount-1;
		}
	}
	const int transformDataSize = numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs * sizeof(TransformData);
```

Per vertex `v`, the pool only reserves slots for **extras** (transforms 1..N−1). The first bone lives inline in `SourceVertex::m_firstTransformData`.

| `localVertexTransformCount` | Slots reserved |
|---|---|
| `< 1` | 0 (condition false) |
| `== 1` | 0 (`>1` is false) |
| `> 1` | `count − 1` |

### Allocation + zero-init (1313–1334)

```1313:1334:D:\Code\swg-client-v2\src\engine\client\library\clientSkeletalAnimation\src\shared\appearance\SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp
	m_sourceData = new byte[alloc_size];
	memset(m_sourceData, 0, alloc_size);
	// ...
	m_transformData = (TransformData *)diter;
	diter += transformDataSize;
```

`memset` zeroes every `SourceVertex` field, including `m_extraTransformDataCount` and `m_firstTransformData`.

### Per-vertex fill pass (1337–1384)

```1359:1381:D:\Code\swg-client-v2\src\engine\client\library\clientSkeletalAnimation\src\shared\appearance\SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp
		if (localVertexTransformCount<1)
		{
			sourceVertex.m_firstTransformData.m_transformIndex = 0;
			sourceVertex.m_firstTransformData.m_transformWeight = 0;
		}
		else
		{
			// ...
			sourceVertex.m_extraTransformDataCount = localVertexTransformCount-1;
			
			for (int j = 1; j < localVertexTransformCount; ++j, ++destTransformData)
			{
				// copy extras into pool
			}
		}
```

| Category | `m_firstTransformData` | `m_extraTransformDataCount` | Pool writes (`destTransformData` advance) |
|---|---|---|---|
| **`count < 1`** (1359–1363) | Forced `{index=0, weight=0}` | **0** (memset, never reassigned) | **0** |
| **`count == 1`** (else, 1372) | Mesh transform 0 | **`0`** (explicit) | **0** |
| **`count > 1`** (else, 1372–1380) | Mesh transform 0 | **`count − 1`** | **`count − 1`** |

Self-check at 1384:

```1384:1384:D:\Code\swg-client-v2\src\engine\client\library\clientSkeletalAnimation\src\shared\appearance\SoftwareBlendSkeletalShaderPrimitive.cpp
	WARNING(destTransformData-m_transformData != numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs, ("logic error: TransfromData count [%d] != numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs [%d]", destTransformData-m_transformData, numberOfExtraTransformWeightPairs));
```

If this fires, the pool layout is wrong before any frame runs.

